<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Department</title>
    <link href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .department-header {
            background-color: #1b6ec2;
            color: white;
            padding: 50px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .department-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }

        .department-image img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .department-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #1b6ec2;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 0;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative; /* Ndryshuar nga fixed në relative */
        }

        /* Shtoni stilizime për hapësirën midis seksioneve */
        .section-spacing {
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="department-header">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <h1>Welcome to the Cardiology Department</h1>
            <p>Your heart health is our priority. Learn more about our services and team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container-fluid department-section section-spacing">
        <div class="row">
            <!-- Foto e Departamentit në anën e majtë -->
            <div class="col-md-6 department-image">
                <img src="/images/cardiology.jpg" alt="Cardiology Department" />
            </div>

            <!-- Teksti në anën e djathtë -->
            <div class="col-md-6 department-text">
                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>At the Cardiology Department, we are dedicated to providing comprehensive heart care. Our team of specialists is committed to diagnosing and treating heart conditions with the latest technology and techniques.</p>
                <h2>Our Services</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Cardiac Consultations</li>
                    <li>Diagnostic Testing (ECG, Echocardiogram)</li>
                    <li>Interventional Cardiology</li>
                    <li>Heart Failure Management</li>
                    <li>Cardiac Rehabilitation</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer Section -->
    <div class="container-fluid footer">
        <p class="mb-0">© 2025 Universal Hospital. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>

    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>